### Test Validation: Booking with past date and wrong service
POST {{baseUrl}}/bookings
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer 6|msF0EQXevqUEDxSuOXjyxLIXSLG7W5AFRFypZv6D79ee511d
Accept: application/json

{
    "booking_date": "2020-01-01", 
    "delivery_date": "2020-01-02",
    "notes": "Testing validation",
    "services": [
        { "service_id": 999999, "quantity": -1 }
    ]
}